 supracitado.</p> <p style="text-align: justify;" data-path-to-node="11">&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: right;" data-path-to-node="12">Sum&eacute; - PB, 26 de Novembro de 2025.</p> <p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Vanklin Mikael Carneiro de Souza Silva</strong></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><em>Agente de Contrata&ccedil;&atilde;o</em></p><br><br>LINK DA MATÉRIA <a href="https://getpublic.inf.br/system/publicacao/materia/20251126032311/?link=CMSU" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://getpublic.inf.br/system/publicacao/materia/20251126032311/?link=CMSU</a> ', 'published', '2025-11-26 15:31:42', 0, '2026-02-13 10:53:48', '2026-02-13 10:53:48');
